            </p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>NEP 2020 compliant</li>
              <li>Grade-specific content</li>
              <li>Modern curriculum</li>
              <li>Structured format</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/syllabus" class="service-btn">
